                    <span>Being a cynic and a successful business man I had some reservations about this genre of books but this one is exceptionally well written and I read it cover to cover in just a few hours. So if the book only contained a single good idea it would be worth reading. The thing is: This little gem contains more good ideas than I can count, so it is definitely worth the time and money! <BR>"First impressions" is great not because it contains useful advice but also because it makes me think about the way I interact with clients and that alone is useful.<BR>Great book, highly recommended.</span>
                  
              
